# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Internal planning / strategy docs — LOCAL ONLY, never published to git.
# The entire docs/ folder is ignored (PLAN, BUSINESS_PLAN, RESUME_BULLETS, TODO).
# Only README.md (root) and the runnable code are tracked.
# To publish a single doc later, un-ignore it explicitly, e.g.:  !docs/PUBLIC.md
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
docs/

